import { Helmet, HelmetProvider } from "react-helmet-async"
import Header from "./Header"
import Slider from "./Slider"

const Reservation = () =>{

    return(
        <HelmetProvider>
            <Helmet>
                <title>Reservation</title>
            </Helmet>
            <Header></Header>
            <Slider></Slider>
        </HelmetProvider>
    )
}
